            <title><![CDATA[베르누이 분포, 기하 분포]]></title>
            <link>https://gracefullight.dev/pe/algo/bernoulli-geometric-distribution/</link>
            <guid>https://gracefullight.dev/pe/algo/bernoulli-geometric-distribution/</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 05:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Bernoulli and Geometric Distribution]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_n3DU" id="베르누이-분포와-기하-분포-개념-비교">베르누이 분포와 기하 분포 개념 비교<a class="hash-link" aria-label="베르누이 분포와 기하 분포 개념 비교에 대한 직접 링크" title="베르누이 분포와 기하 분포 개념 비교에 대한 직접 링크" href="https://gracefullight.dev/pe/algo/bernoulli-geometric-distribution/#%EB%B2%A0%EB%A5%B4%EB%88%84%EC%9D%B4-%EB%B6%84%ED%8F%AC%EC%99%80-%EA%B8%B0%ED%95%98-%EB%B6%84%ED%8F%AC-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90">​</a></h2>
<table><thead><tr><th>베르누이 분포</th><th>기하 분포</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>상호 배반인 두가지 가능한 결과 중 하나를 가지는 베르누이 시행을 나타내는 확률 분포</td><td>독립적인 베르누이 시행을 여러번 수행할 때 처음 성공까지 시도한 횟수의 분포</td></tr></tbody></table>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_n3DU" id="베르누이-분포와-기하분포-상세-비교">베르누이 분포와 기하분포 상세 비교<a class="hash-link" aria-label="베르누이 분포와 기하분포 상세 비교에 대한 직접 링크" title="베르누이 분포와 기하분포 상세 비교에 대한 직접 링크" href="https://gracefullight.dev/pe/algo/bernoulli-geometric-distribution/#%EB%B2%A0%EB%A5%B4%EB%88%84%EC%9D%B4-%EB%B6%84%ED%8F%AC%EC%99%80-%EA%B8%B0%ED%95%98%EB%B6%84%ED%8F%AC-%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90">​</a></h2>
<table><thead><tr><th>구분</th><th>베르누이 분포</th><th>기하 분포</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>수식</td><td>성공확률 P, 실패확률 1-P</td><td>예상치 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">E(X) = 1/P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em">E</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em">X</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em"></span><span class="mord">1/</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em">P</span></span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td>-</td><td>평균 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">E(X) = P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em">E</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em">X</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em">P</span></span></span></span></td><td>분산 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>p</mi></mrow><msup><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Var(X) = \frac{1-p}{p^2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">Va</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em">r</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em">X</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.3783em;vertical-align:-0.4811em"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8972em"><span style="top:-2.655em"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">p</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.7463em"><span style="top:-2.786em;margin-right:0.0714em"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em"></span></span><span style="top:-3.4461em"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">p</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.4811em"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></td></tr><tr><td>-</td><td>분산 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>p</mi><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Var(X) = p(1 - p) = pq</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">Va</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em">r</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em">X</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em">pq</span></span></span></span></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>사례</td><td>동전 뒤집기</td><td>타율이 3할인 선수가 두번째 타석에서 홈런칠 확률</td></tr></tbody></table>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_n3DU" id="베르누이-분포와-기하분포-사용">베르누이 분포와 기하분포 사용<a class="hash-link" aria-label="베르누이 분포와 기하분포 사용에 대한 직접 링크" title="베르누이 분포와 ��기하분포 사용에 대한 직접 링크" href="https://gracefullight.dev/pe/algo/bernoulli-geometric-distribution/#%EB%B2%A0%EB%A5%B4%EB%88%84%EC%9D%B4-%EB%B6%84%ED%8F%AC%EC%99%80-%EA%B8%B0%ED%95%98%EB%B6%84%ED%8F%AC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li>확률 모델링과 추론에 사용</li>
<li>빅데이터 분석의 확률 통계, 정보 이론 등에 사용</li>
</ul>]]></content:encoded>
